text: This event is dispatched when the user changes something, for instance, updates a configuration. The following fields are included: userName - The name of the user. userAction - Action performed by the user. Fields inherited from the Base event The following fields are inherited from the Base event, and described in more detail in Base Event : category contents - Username: <username>, Action: <action>, Workflow: <Workflow name> eventName origin receiveTimeStamp severity timeStamp
title: User Event - MediationZone Documentation 9.3 - InfoZone
